Beep is platform that allows users to tokenize Naira, transfer tokens, withdraw Naira, and create an intent to exchange Naira for tAtom tokens. This platform enables seamless transactions and interactions with tokenized assets.

Features

Tokenize Naira: Users can deposit Naira and receive an equivalent amount of Beep tokens.

Transfer Tokens: Users can transfer Beep tokens to other users.

Withdraw Naira: Convert Beep tokens back to Naira and withdraw to a bank account.

Create Intent for tAtom: Users can create an intent to exchange Naira for tAtom tokens.

Tech Stack

Backend: Node.js, Express.js

Database: MongoDB 

Authentication: JWT (JSON Web Tokens)

Blockchain Integration: cosmos SDK, cosmos.js

Installation & Setup

Prerequisites

Node.js & npm installed

MongoDB o

.env file configured with required environment variables

Steps to Run Locally

Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/come-senusi-wale/beep-hackar.git
cd beep-api

Install dependencies:
npm install

Create a .env file and configure:

PORT=5000
MONGODB_URI=your mongo db url
RPC=https://rpc-palvus.pion-1.ntrn.tech
ENCRYTION_KEY=9999
TERMI_API_KEY=
TERMII_SENDER_ID=
TOKEN_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=neutron1ujaf3dgpgn7e5tg6xy2hfnx6a6aupzjgxgj8fust08jttv03059s2jv2uw
BEEP_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=neutron1rvn3dawaze4qyv7p9h4mcyll5axs0tefu90fdmw0s8u5wzaxjqhqc2m3gx
TOKEN_ATOM_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=neutron17huqemgnu8r4092z74vu5jtzgm3lxg4gzqupu48648t8fz4wyzxsy7rjkf
TOKEN_NGN_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=neutron1ujaf3dgpgn7e5tg6xy2hfnx6a6aupzjgxgj8fust08jttv03059s2jv2uw
